### English Reading Tool

#### Std II level text

The sun was hot. The boy was thirsty. He saw a well. He drank water from the well. He was happy.

#### Std I level text

The cat is fat. The rat is fat. The cat eats the rat.

#### Capital letters

A B C
D E F
G H I

#### Small letters

a b c
d e f
g h i

#### Simple words

cat
dog
hat
mat
pot
sun
run
fun

#### Easy sentences

The cat is fat.
The dog is big.
The sun is hot.
The rain is wet.

